# Requests

Here are some examples of how you might get Ginger resources.

    import Ginger.Request as Request
        exposing
            ( Ordering(..)
            , QueryParam(..)
            , SortField(..)
            )

    query : Cmd Msg
    query =
        Request.resourceQuery GotSearchResults
            [ Text "amsterdam" ]

    events : Cmd Msg
    events =
        Request.resourceQuery GotEvents
            [ Upcoming
            , HasCategory Event
            , SortBy StartDate Asc
            ]

